# base-webctl .gitignore
# Canonical secret-free template — this is the SAME block base prescribes for all
# *-webctl tools in docs/design/infra-directory-structure-f868.md ("Gitignore
# Patterns"). base must follow its own spec: secrets/session-state NEVER enter git.

# Configuration with secrets
.env.*
*.env
credentials*
cookies*

# Track example templates (the only dotenv/config files that ARE committed)
!dotenv.*.example

# Runtime artifacts
tmp/
cache/
screenshots/
output/
phenomena/
debug.log

# Dependencies and build
node_modules/
package-lock.json

# IDE / tool state
.claude/
.worktrees/
